    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName ref="#people/118"
                            key="#Commutatio #Emperor/king">Hludovicus</persName> divina ordinante
                        providentia <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Omnibus …
                            <persName ref="#people/119"
                            key="#Commutatio #Churches #Baptismal_churches #Monasteries #Abbots"
                            >Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> venerabilis <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/15" key="#Monasteries"
                                ><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/47"
                                key="#Commutatio #Churches #Baptismal_churches #Abbots"
                                >Nonantule</orgName></placeName>, quod est constructum … quoddam <rs
                            key="#Commutatio">pactum</rs> confirmationis inter ipsum et <persName
                            key="#Commutatio #Churches #Baptismal_churches"
                            ref="#people/152">Gisonem</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopum</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/38" key="#Mother_churches"
                            >Motinensis</placeName>
                        <orgName key="#Commutatio #Churches #Baptismal_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/96">aecclesiae</orgName>
                        … de <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiis</rs> … unum in quo legebatur, quod dedit
                        … ipse abbas ex parte monasterii … cum omnibus pertinentiis suis prope
                            <placeName>Lama</placeName> ad partem aecclesiae Motinensis pro cunctis
                            <rs key="#Baptismal_churches">aecclesiis baptismalibus</rs> .. et rebus
                        predictis. Et obligaverunt [..] Signum M Hludovici serenissimi imperatoris …
                        recognovi et subscripsi SI. <date>Data … anno sexto Christo propritio
                            imperii nostri, indictione duodecima</date> …</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
